Interface XAttributable

All Known Subinterfaces:
XAttribute, XAttributeBoolean, XAttributeContinuous, XAttributeDiscrete, XAttributeLiteral, XAttributeTimestamp, XElement, XEvent, XLog, XTrace
All Known Implementing Classes:
XAttributeBooleanImpl, XAttributeContinuousImpl, XAttributeDiscreteImpl, XAttributeImpl, XAttributeLiteralImpl, XAttributeTimestampImpl, XEventImpl, XExtendedEvent, XLogImpl, XTraceBufferedImpl, XTraceImpl
public interface XAttributable

This interface is implemented by all elements of the log hierarchy, which can be equipped with attributes.

Author:
Christian W. Guenther (christian@deckfour.org)
